# DealRoom v3 — Architecture (Updated)

> **Document status:** Reflects implemented state plus four required fixes.
> Working sections describe exactly what is built. Fix sections specify
> exactly what needs to change. Do not modify working sections.

---

## Overview

DealRoom v3 is a multi-stakeholder enterprise negotiation RL environment.
A vendor agent negotiates with a committee of 6 stakeholders (Legal, Finance,
TechLead, Procurement, Operations, ExecSponsor) across three scenario types:
`aligned`, `conflicted`, `hostile_acquisition`.

OpenEnv-compatible: `reset()` → observation, `step(action)` → observation +
reward + done + info. FastAPI HTTP server. Pure-Python deterministic reward.
MiniMax-only LLM for natural language generation (not scoring).

