| Finance | 0.15 | 0.50 | **True** |
| TechLead | 0.25 | 0.30 | False |
| Procurement | 0.20 | 0.45 | False |
| Operations | 0.30 | 0.35 | False |
| ExecSponsor | 0.40 | 0.25 | **True** |

Core research claim verified: Legal + no DPA → EU > 0 but CVaR > 0.10 = tau.
