## Step Pipeline (Current State with Fix Positions)

```
step(action):
  [1]  lookahead_was_requested = extract(action.lookahead)    ← FIRST LINE ✅
  [2]  state_before = StateSnapshot(self._state)              ← before mutations ✅
  [3]  LookaheadSimulator.simulate()                         ← FIX #3 (medium)
  [4]  _bayesian_update() × all stakeholders                 ✅
  [5]  CommitteeDeliberationEngine.run()                      ✅
         Layer 1: propagate_beliefs()   [pure Python, always]
         Layer 2: _generate_summary()   [MiniMax 5s, display only]
  [6]  _update_noisy_engagement()                             ✅
  [7]  _generate_stakeholder_responses()                      ✅
  [8]  _check_veto_termination()                             ← FIX #1 (critical)
  [9]  _compute_reward(action, state_before, lookahead)       ✅
  [10] _build_observation(responses=responses)               ← FIX #2 (high)
  [11] return (obs, reward, done, info)
```

